rComments: Carly was a fantastic professor. Her lectures were quite interesting and fun to sit through. 3 hours felt like 1 hour and she brought the course material to life. Loved taking this course and would happily take another course with her.

Carly is a very caring prof, however, a very slow grader. If you want your papers and tests back quick, don't take the course. She is very easy to approach and accommodating. There are a lot of group projects and assignments, which can be good for some people but also a drawback for others.
